Richard Vidutis: He ran a tough ship, stripped ship to faculty, and departments.

63
00:05:57.940 --> 00:06:06.619
Richard Vidutis: Everybody knew that, and they were careful not to get him upset, so… That's how he was,

64
00:06:07.190 --> 00:06:12.290
Richard Vidutis: I don't think you produced 20 books in, I don't know, 100 articles or whatever it was, with

65
00:06:13.710 --> 00:06:16.909
Richard Vidutis: By not being really strict and demanding.

66
00:06:17.590 --> 00:06:19.830
Richard Vidutis: Yeah, that really was his style.

67
00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:23.440
Richard Vidutis: I came across a photo

68
00:06:23.800 --> 00:06:28.589
Richard Vidutis: And I misplaced it again. I took in the… in the office.

69
00:06:28.950 --> 00:06:33.649
