74
00:06:49.540 --> 00:06:54.150
Richard Vidutis: Carefully listening to him, not missing anything. They didn't want to upset him.

75
00:06:54.740 --> 00:06:56.049
Richard Vidutis: So, yeah.

76
00:06:58.860 --> 00:07:07.530
Julie Stout: I think that's a great, like, overview of seeing his interactions with other people, and also representing his personality at the same time. Would you agree?

