82
00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:36.520
Richard Vidutis: The other one's, like,

83
00:07:37.090 --> 00:07:44.580
Richard Vidutis: Seward and Cooley and Benadunas in March, they obviously had to meet with Dawson and talk about what

