93
00:08:27.580 --> 00:08:34.260
Richard Vidutis: For some reason, universities don't… Folklore faculties don't seem to do team kind of,

94
00:08:34.870 --> 00:08:39.650
Richard Vidutis: investigations into communities. It's usually just individuals

95
00:08:40.850 --> 00:08:47.280
Richard Vidutis: that's one of the reasons why I really enjoy working for FEMA, or when I worked,

96
00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:50.549
Richard Vidutis: for CRM, Cultural Resource Management.

97
00:08:51.420 --> 00:08:54.730
Richard Vidutis: They're all always teams. They're always working with.

98
00:08:54.840 --> 00:09:01.270
