112
00:10:16.470 --> 00:10:21.420
Richard Vidutis: Or he was also teaching at Northwest Indiana University.

113
00:10:21.830 --> 00:10:25.100
Richard Vidutis: So, he wasn't with us all the time, but

114
00:10:25.700 --> 00:10:29.580
Richard Vidutis: He kept a strict… a strict leash on everybody.

115
00:10:29.690 --> 00:10:30.619
Richard Vidutis: I thought.

116
00:10:30.800 --> 00:10:32.280
